tip.text: half of this space is Hardcore Interactive Gaming Hub (LAN gaming) - expect to be serenaded with gunfire and spells. kid's toy corner of the cafe is an interesting counterpoint, if odd.
Boon Tong Kee Braised Duck Rice looked good, but the duck meat tasted bland. do not want again.
Braised Short Ribs is going to disappear from the menu in July 2013. get it while it lasts!
